# ==========================================
# FinPulse Global .gitignore Configuration
# ==========================================

# --- Java & Maven ---
**/target/
**/pom.xml.tag
**/pom.xml.releaseBackup
**/pom.xml.versionsBackup
**/pom.xml.next
**/release.properties
**/dependency-reduced-pom.xml
**/.flattened-pom.xml
**/classhelper.properties

# --- Node & Frontend ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.eslintcache
**/.yarn-integrity
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnp/
**/.pnp.js

# --- Environment Configuration (Secrets) ---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local
**/*.env.local
**/.env*.local

# --- IDE & Editors ---
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.ipr
**/*.iws
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings/
**/.factorypath
**/.vscode/
**/*.sublime-project
**/*.sublime-workspace
**/.history/
**/.direnv/

# --- Operating System & Temporary Files ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*~
*.swp
*.bak
*.tmp
*.log
**/logs/
**/log/

# --- Infrastructure & GitOps (Terraform, Helm, Docker) ---
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/charts/*-charts/*.tgz
**/.dockertemp/
**/*.dockercache/

# --- E2E Testing (Playwright) ---
**/test-results/
**/playwright-report/
**/blob-report/
**/.playwright/
